{"article_id":"tSYOLrAq0lZCxpBx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In April , President Obama announced the framework of a deal","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"would prevent Iran from obtaining a nuclear weapon .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"\" We only have three options","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"for addressing Iran ' s nuclear program \"","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"--","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"cutting a deal with Iran ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"\" starting another war in the Middle East \"","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"or \" hope for the best . \"","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"In deploying his favorite rhetorical device ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"the president reaffirmed to the world","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"he only really saw one option :","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"cutting a deal with Iran","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"no matter the cost .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"If after witnessing six years of President Obama ' s weak and feckless foreign policy wasn ' t enough","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to embolden the regime in Tehran ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"President Obama ' s comments in April must have convinced the mullahs","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"they had the American president right where they wanted him .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The price for President Obama ' s penchant","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"for negotiating from weakness","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"is now clear .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The deal","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"announced with much fanfare by the White House two weeks ago","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"comes nowhere close to the deal","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"President Obama promised the American people","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"he ' d get .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Far from the promise","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"of preventing \" Iran from obtaining a nuclear weapon , \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"the deal","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"brokered by President Obama and Secretaries of State Hillary Clinton and John Kerry","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"guarantees","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that the world ' s foremost state sponsor of terror will be a nuclear threshold state in the next 15 years , but probably much sooner .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The details of the breadth and scope of President Obama ' s capitulations to Tehran are startling , even by his standards .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"But most alarming of all is the realization","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"that President Obama decided to elevate an evil and illegitimate third-rate autocracy .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"In order to ensure","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"that the damage","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"done by President Obama","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"can be repaired ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"we need to learn the lessons of his failures .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"They began","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"long before he reached the White House ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"when during his campaign for the presidency he announced his willingness","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to meet ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"without preconditions ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"with the leaders of Iran , Syria , Venezuela , Cuba and North Korea .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"When American presidents speak ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"leaders around the world ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"both friends and foes , listen .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"And the listening begins","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"long before the president is sworn into office .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"In addition , how","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"candidates","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"aspiring for the presidency","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"now talk about Iran will send a clear signal to the world about their foreign policy vision .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Our allies and adversaries alike want to know","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"whether America will continue the retreat from the world","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"begun by President Obama and Secretary of State Hillary Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"or will America return to its indispensable leadership role in the world ?","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Making that case begins now ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"by making it clear to the American people and the world","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that this is President Obama ' s deal with Iran , not America ' s deal with Iran .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The next President must campaign for the office on the principle","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that has long guided American foreign policy toward Iran","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"- that the regime can not have mastery of dangerous nuclear technologies .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Period .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"The next president must re-impose the sanctions","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"waived by President Obama","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"and work with Congress","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"to impose new crushing sanctions on Iran ' s leaders for their ongoing support for terrorism and brutal human rights abuses .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"This will require engagement with our European allies","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"to lead them toward a different approach to Iran than the Obama-Clinton approach .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Part of this reengagement must make it clear","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that European security does not benefit","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"by empowering Iran ' s terrorist proxies and missiles","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"that can hit Europe ' s cities .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"But the rest of the world also needs to realize","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"if Europe intends to pursue a strategy","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that empowers an unreformed Iran ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"America will put our security interests first .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"The next president must give Iran a choice :","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"change your behavior ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"or face the collapse of your economy due to U.S. pressure .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Despite its inflammatory rhetoric ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Iran ' s clerical dictatorship has immense vulnerabilities .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Iran ' s economy continues to suffer from inflation and unemployment","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"while rampant corruption plagues the state at all levels .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"A strategy of pressure will not just focus on Iran ' s economy ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"but also its regional position .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"For Iran ' s leaders to make painful concessions","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"they have avoided thus far ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"they need to understand","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that there are consequences for their actions .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"The U.S. should undertake a systematic effort","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"to isolate Iran in the Middle East .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"The Islamic Republic , its clients and proxies , should find no sanctuary in the region .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"The U.S. must do all","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"it can","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"to counter Iran ' s nefarious plots in places like Iraq , Lebanon , Gaza , Syria or Yemen .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"This will be advanced","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"by shoring up our alliance with Israel .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"The first step will be an end to the threatening rhetoric from senior U.S. officials","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"warning of Israeli isolation","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"and dismissing Israeli government leaders","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"\" who know what they ' re talking about . \"","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"President Obama ' s capitulation has made it more difficult , but not impossible , to prevent a nuclear Iran .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"He has failed with Iran","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"because he has failed as president .","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"This may be the best deal","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"that a weak president can achieve ,","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"but a strong , trusted and respected America can do much better .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"Those","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"who aspire to lead the greatest nation on Earth","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"can not wait until 2017","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"to begin making the case for a new approach toward this critical issue to the American people , and the world .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":223,"right":232,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":152,"right":222,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":135,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":131,"right":134,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":120,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":125,"right":129,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":121,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":7,"right":122,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":10,"right":128,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":11,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nu